song_name: Do You Know How It Feels

version_description: No Capo and original key. All credit to this guy.. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GSpviJteGiI.

They play these chords on the Guilded Palace of Sin version (the only version I know). Strumming pattern is down, down-up, down-up, on a 1, 2-and, 3-and count. After the last E chord of every verse, I do another measure of E with my pinkie on the B string at the 3d fret to transition into the verse. Don't know what to call that chord. I do the same thing after the E chord at the end of the first line of the chorus.
